com.kontakt.sdk.android.common.model

Class Preset

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.common.model.Preset
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class Preset
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Preset describes the predefined set of parameters that Device can be configured with. Contrary to Config, presets are not removed once the device will be updated with parameters applied from them. They should be interpreted as states in which devices are working. For example, you could define "Long interval profile" where device interval period accepts the the longest interval.
